data.value: This draft dataset is of SIPPER (Shadow Image Particle Profiling and Evaluation Recorder) images and associated environmental and navigation data collected as part of the NRDA cooperative sampling effort in 2010 of the Deepwater Horizon oil spill of national significance. This dataset was processed and classified by principal investigator Dr. Andrew Remsen and software engineer Dr. Kurt Kramer.
